---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Yu Ho">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Yu Ho, a software engineer based in China. I build tools, tinker with
      my homelab, and write about the things I learn along the way.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Do</h2>

    <p>
      By day, I work as a software engineer. In my spare time, I maintain a
      Synology NAS running a dozen Docker services, experiment with AI assistants,
      and contribute to open source.
    </p>

    <h2>This Site</h2>

    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, styled with
      <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind CSS</a>, deployed on
      <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com">Cloudflare Pages</a>.
      Images hosted on Cloudflare R2.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/yuho">@yuho</a></li>
      <li>Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/yuho">@yuho</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
